<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink339">
<l>amma vāḻi toḻi ciṟiyilaik</l>
<l>kuṟuñciṉai vēmpi ṉaṟumpaḻa muṇīiya</l>
<l>vāva  lukakku mālaiyu</l>
<l>miṉṟuko ṟōḻiyavar ceṉṟa nāṭṭē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Alas! May you live long, my friend! </l>
<l>In the land to which he has gone, </l>
<l>are there no evenings when bats ascend, </l>
<l>feasting on the fragrant fruits of the Neem tree, </l>
<l>with its small leaves and short branches? [Tell me], my friend! </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
